Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:15.23,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,Faced with monsters \Nimmune to modern weaponry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.54,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,humanity was pushed to \Nthe brink of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.62,Main,Puppets,0,0,0,,Dear God, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.38,Main,Puppets,0,0,0,,Please save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:26.64,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(1630,1)\bord0\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\b1\pos(320,20)}Thus, {\alpha&FF&}gods {\alpha&00&}appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:26.64,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(1840,1)\bord0\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\b1\pos(320,20)\alpha&FF&}Thus, {\alpha&00&\c&HB5FBFC&}gods {\alpha&FF&\c&HFFFFFF&}appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.14,Italics,Narr,0,0,0,,They were battle deities called Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:37.10,Italics,Narr,0,0,0,,They arrived suddenly, \Ndefeating the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.27,Main,Grandfather,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:44.53,Italics,Narr,0,0,0,,...and then sealing them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:49.19,Italics,Narr,0,0,0,,These events occurred over 800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:54.33,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Grandfather! Why do you all \Nhave to sacrifice yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.46,Main,Grandfather,0,0,0,,There's no other way to ensure \Nthe seal is effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:02.96,Main,Grandfather,0,0,0,,We will travel to the other side, \Nsouls and all, and become part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.99,Main,Friend,0,0,0,,Rin, you're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:06.71,Main,Friend,0,0,0,,Keep living and watch over the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:10.93,Main,Friend,0,0,0,,Share your strength with the gods\N who have yet to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:16.81,Main,Sukis,0,0,0,,And if anything happens to the seal, \Nit's your job to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.94,Main,Sukis,0,0,0,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.86,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.84,Main,Grandfather,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.59,Main,Grandfather,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:38.39,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,No! Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:53.05,Show_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4409,938)\fscy140}The Idaten {\c&H21FCFB&}Dei{\c&H2601D4&}ties\N{\fs24\c&H19F7D8&\i0\3c&H3E679B&\fscy100}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hKn{\c&HD6E1F9&}ow {\c&H19F7D8&}On{\c&HD6E1F9&}ly {\c&H19F7D8&}Pe{\c&HD6E1F9&}ac{\c&H19F7D8&}e
